  "slug": "anointed-items",
  "title": "Anointed Items",
  "description": "Adds a mechanic to add attributes to gear! (maxhealth, attack speed, and more!)",
  "body": "<p><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: 'arial black', sans-serif;\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/TFS7L3P.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"690\" height=\"108\"></span></strong></span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12px;\">It introduces an alternative method of enhancing your gear different from the normal enchanting process. It is highly configurable and compatible with almost every mod.</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 12px;\">&nbsp;<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/bcGogIY.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"696\" height=\"21\"></span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 12px;\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/if37ezS.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"603\" height=\"62\"></span></p>\n<p>Firstly it introduces a brand-new GUI accessible through the <strong>Anointing Table</strong>. This mod adds six types of oil that can be crafted from various materials found in vanilla Minecraft. The Anointing Table works in a way similar to the <strong>Smithing Table</strong> and <strong>Anvil </strong>which makes it&nbsp;user-friendly. The initial item selected should be the one for crafting, followed by the chosen oil as the secondary input. It's important to note that items cannot exceed <strong>Tier IV</strong>.</p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12px;\">Crafting an&nbsp;<strong>Anointing Table</strong> table requires the following:</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12px;\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/2uBE4Ik.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"223\" height=\"119\"></span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 12px;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12px;\">When opened its GUI will look like this:</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12px;\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/pem77eX.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"358\" height=\"326\"></span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 12px;\">&nbsp;<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/bcGogIY.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"696\" height=\"21\"></span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 12px;\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/Vk8b4ML.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"162\" height=\"63\"><br></span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 12px;\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">&lt;&gt; Acceleration Oil:</span></strong></span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12px;\">- Increases your item tier by 1.</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12px;\">- Adds +0.5 mining speed to your item. (Configurable.)</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 12px;\"><em><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/teabAh9.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"295\" height=\"144\"></span></em></span></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12px;\"><strong>&lt;&gt; Agility Oil:</strong></span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12px;\">- Increases your item tier by 1.</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12px;\">- Adds +0.02 movement speed to your item (Seen as +0.2 on tooltip). (Configurable.)</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12px;\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/P2D5iQx.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"295\" height=\"144\"></span></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12px;\"><strong>&lt;&gt; Lightness Oil:</strong></span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12px;\">- Increases your item tier by 1.</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12px;\">- Adds +0.2 attack speed to your item.&nbsp;(Configurable.)</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12px;\"><em><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/ZosNaxE.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"295\" height=\"144\"></em></span></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><strong style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12px;\">&lt;&gt; Power Oil:</strong></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12px;\">- Increases your item tier by 1.</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12px;\">- Adds +1 attack damage to your item. (Configurable.)</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12px;\"><em><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/3gQ8BFQ.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"295\" height=\"144\"></em></span></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12px;\"><strong>&lt;&gt; Protection Oil:</strong></span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12px;\">- Increases your item tier by 1.</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12px;\">- Adds +1 armor to your item.&nbsp;(Configurable.)</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 12px;\"><em><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/cMAZStM.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"295\" height=\"144\"></em></span></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12px;\"><strong>&lt;&gt; Tenacity Oil:</strong></span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12px;\">- Increases your item tier by 1.</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12px;\">- Adds +1 max health to your item.&nbsp;(Configurable.)</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 12px;\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/1CI7mgT.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"295\" height=\"144\"></span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 12px;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 12px;\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/lbMFSy6.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"552\" height=\"21\"></span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 12px;\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/uebNd42.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"226\" height=\"62\"></span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 12px; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><strong>Example Item</strong></span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 12px;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">As you can see this netherite pickaxe is anointed with 3 acceleration oils and 1 agility oil. A</span><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">lso name changes from anvil get auto-fixed by this mod.</span></span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 12px;\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: 'arial black', sans-serif;\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/NqlHk8c.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"285\" height=\"212\"></span></strong></span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12px;\">You can use this mod in your modpacks freely.</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12px;\">STOP REPOSTING! I DON'T ALLOW MY MOD TO BE REUPLOADED ON ANYWHERE ELSE FOR NO REASON.</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12px;\">&nbsp;</span></p>",
